rComments: Amazing Prof, teaches very well and is willing to modify the course content to fit in modern-world trade issues. Very helpful.

The course is very easy, as long as you do all the problem sets you will definitely get an A! The explanations are very clear, the professor is very passionate and he adds a lot of empirical details. I only wish he used more the blackboard and a bit less the slides. Recommended overall!
A great prof! Very interesting topics, good explainer, interesting models and theories. You have to be prepared to do work if you want a good grade, but it's worth it. Highly recommend this prof.
Poor slides, bad explainer, tough to get much out of this class.
Slides are terrible. Not clear solutions. Hard to follow.

Nice instructor, good lectures.  He posts everything online (lecture notes, practice problems).  Master practice problems and you should be ok.. he can throw a curve ball at you in the final, so make sure you studying EVERYTHING!
